rComments: Great professor. She really cares about her students and is deeply invested in her field of study!
She is really nice and care for her students. This course was really interesting! She gives attendance points (for group discussion, small quiz...)

This prof is clearly new but it doesn't hinder her teaching skills. She is honestly so nice and approachable, and will even apologize for "talking too long" or "keeping us too long" even though she's just doing what she should be. Everyone in class talks about how adorable it is. The material isn't exactly interesting but she does what she can.
